      "review_title": "Just Okay",
      "review_description": "As a free substitute for the other more well-known and beloved game, it's..just okay. You can only stand in one spot essentially with a few virtual feet to walk/turn. I didn't see any settings menu/any menus at all, but devs please correct me if I'm wrong about that. I was looking for something kind of easier for my younger children ages 4.5-7 and they will have fun with the game for a few minutes, and seem to like it, however they also wish they could walk around a bit more. Excited to see any future updates and hope this helps. Thanks for the game! ☺️",
